        <div class="msgSubject">Explaining XIV progression system shortcomings through XI</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-14 15:14:42   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1289769282304697954" id="quote-1289769282304697954" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1289769282304697954" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=173&amp;mid=1289769282304697954&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1289769282304697954&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1289769282304697954" onclick="followToggle('add','1289769282304697954')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="msgWhoFrame">
        <div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName " href="/users/Hyanmen">Hyanmen</a></div><div class="msgAvatar"></div><div class="msgStar"><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/></div><div class="msgWhoNum">1,907 posts</div>
